clear all;
close all;
fund = 880;
Fs = 8000;
lll=8192;
ll2=lll/2;
Fpass = 0.24*Fs;
Fstop = 0.26*Fs;
Ap = 1;
Ast = 30;
Avib = 50;
fvib = 5;
d = designfilt('lowpassfir','PassbandFrequency',Fpass,...
'StopbandFrequency',Fstop,'PassbandRipple',Ap,...
'StopbandAttenuation',Ast,'SampleRate',Fs);
temps =[0:1/Fs:1];
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% definition du signal x %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
% x = cos(2*pi*fund*temps) + cos(2*pi*2*fund*temps) + cos(2*pi*3*fund*temps) + cos(2*pi*4*fund*temps);
x = cos(2*pi*fund*temps + (Avib/fvib)*sin(2*pi*fvib*temps)) + cos(2*pi*2*fund*temps + (2*Avib/fvib)*sin(2*pi*fvib*temps)) + cos(2*pi*3*fund*temps + (3*Avib/fvib)*sin(2*pi*fvib*temps)) + cos(2*pi*4*fund*temps + (3*Avib/fvib)*sin(2*pi*fvib*temps));
% audiowrite('first.wav',x,Fs);
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% spectrogramme du signal x %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
tfen=0.04;lfen=round(Fs*tfen);
[Sspec, fspec, tspec] = specgram(x, lll, Fs, hanning(lfen), lfen-round(Fs*0.005));
figure(1);
clf;
imagesc(tspec+tfen/2, fspec, (log10(abs(Sspec))));
title('spectrogramme du signal avec fenetre de 40 ms','Fontsize',18);
grid on;
xlabel('temps (s)','Fontsize',20);
ylabel('frequence (Hz)','Fontsize',20);
hold off;
print -depsc2 nstat2_exe2_tfct.eps
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% filtrage de x ====> y %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
y=filtfilt(d.Coefficients,1,x);
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Transformée de Fourier de x ====> TF_x %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
TF_x=fft(x,lll);
TF_x=fftshift(TF_x);
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Transformée de Fourier de y -- TF_y %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
TF_y=fft(y,lll);
TF_y=fftshift(TF_y);
freq=([0:lll-1]-lll/2)*Fs/lll;
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Traçage de x, TF_x %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
figure(2);
clf;
title('Signal de depart','Fontsize',18);
subplot(2,1,1);
plot(temps,x)
subplot(2,1,2);
plot(freq,abs(TF_x),'Linewidth',2);
hold off;
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Traçage de y et TF_y %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
figure(3);
clf;
subplot(2,1,1);
plot(temps,y)
subplot(2,1,2);
plot(freq,abs(TF_y),'Linewidth',2);
hold off;
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% sous échantillonnage de y ====> y_ss %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
y_ss = y(1:2:end);
temps2 =[0:length(y_ss)-1]/(Fs/2);
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Transformée de Fourier de y_ss ====> TF_y_ss %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
TF_y_ss=fft(y_ss,lll);
TF_y_ss=fftshift(TF_y_ss);
freq1=([0:lll-1]-lll/2)*(Fs/2)/lll;
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Traçage de y_ss (y sous échantillonné ) et TF_y_ss %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
figure(5);
clf;
subplot(2,1,1);
plot(temps2,y_ss)
subplot(2,1,2);
plot(freq1,abs(TF_y_ss),'Linewidth',2);
hold off;
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% definition de la nouvelle frequence d'echantillonnage et le nouveau filtre %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
Fs1 = Fs/2;
Fpass1 = 0.24*Fs1;
Fstop1 = 0.26*Fs1;
d1 = designfilt('lowpassfir','PassbandFrequency',Fpass1,...
'StopbandFrequency',Fstop1,'PassbandRipple',Ap,...
'StopbandAttenuation',Ast,'SampleRate',Fs1);
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% filtrage de y_ss ====> z %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
z = filtfilt(d1.Coefficients,1,y_ss);
TF_z=fft(z,lll);
TF_z=fftshift(TF_z);
freq2=([0:lll-1]-lll/2)*Fs1/lll;
temps3 = [0:length(z)-1]/(Fs1/2);
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Traçage de z, TF_z %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
figure(6);
clf;
subplot(2,1,1);
plot(temps3,z)
subplot(2,1,2);
plot(freq2,abs(TF_z),'Linewidth',2);
hold off;
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% sous échantillonnage de z ====> z_ss %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
z_ss = z(1:2:end);
%audiowrite('last1.wav',z_ss,Fs);
temps3 =[0:length(z_ss)-1]/(Fs1/2);
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Transformée de Fourier de z_ss ====> TF_z_ss %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
TF_z_ss=fft(z_ss,lll);
TF_z_ss=fftshift(TF_z_ss);
freq2=([0:lll-1]-lll/2)*(Fs1/2)/lll;
%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%% Traçage de z_ss (z sous échantillonné ) et TF_z_ss %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
figure(7);
clf;
subplot(2,1,1);
plot(temps3,z_ss)
subplot(2,1,2);
plot(freq2,abs(TF_z_ss),'Linewidth',2);
hold off;
